# Unique arithmetic sentinel: 5432*1759 = 9554888 -- a distinctive product that will
# NOT appear in a page by chance and is NEVER the literal payload (so its presence in
# the response proves the template engine EVALUATED the expression, not just reflected
# it). Methodology follows the PayloadsAllTheThings SSTI decision tree + the
# payload-box/ssti-advanced-payload-list and the Java EL/SpEL/OGNL injection notes.
